OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: I feel I am serving a
OL,4,Csentence for a crime I did not commit
OL,6,FScotland's former first minister
OL,7,FNicola Sturgeon said she feels like
OL,8,Fshe is "serving a sentence for a crime
OL,9,FI did not commit" after her estranged
OL,10,Fhusband, former SNP chief executive
OL,11,FPeter Murrell, admitted embezzling
OL,12,Fmore than #400,000 from the party.
OL,14,FMurrell pleaded guilty this week to
OL,15,Fembezzling the sum from the SNP
OL,16,Fbetween 2010 and 2022.
OL,26,@pD@HOUqD@QO]
