OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780229466
OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: I feel I am serving a
OL,4,Csentence for a crime I did not commit
OL,6,FThe 61-year-old spent the money on
OL,7,Fitems including a motorhome, cars,
OL,8,Fkitchen gadgets, expensive watches and
OL,9,Fpens, and more mundane purchases such
OL,10,Fas hand cream and toilet seats.
OL,12,FHe is set to be sentenced in June, the
OL,13,Fsame month that the SNP faces two by-
OL,14,Felection contests ` one in Aberdeen
OL,15,FSouth and another in Arbroath and
OL,16,FBroughty Ferry.
OL,18,FThe SNP has faced calls for an
OL,19,Findependent inquiry into its finances.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
