OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: I feel I am serving a
OL,4,Csentence for a crime I did not commit
OL,6,FMs Sturgeon was Scotland's first
OL,7,Fminister from 2014 to 2023 while
OL,8,FMurrell served as the SNP chief
OL,9,Fexecutive from 2001 to 2023.
OL,11,FIn an interview on the BBC's Sunday
OL,12,Fwith Laura Kuenssberg programme, Ms
OL,13,FSturgeon said she is "not going to
OL,14,Fapologise for somebody else's crimes".
OL,26,@uD@VOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
