CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780229466
OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: I feel I am serving a
OL,4,Csentence for a crime I did not commit
OL,6,FShe said: "For my own sake, but for
OL,7,Fthe sake of people out there, a lot of
OL,8,Fwomen who end up finding themselves
OL,9,Fblamed for the actions of the men in
OL,10,Ftheir lives, I'm not going to
OL,11,Fcontribute to that kind of sense that
OL,12,FI am responsible for somebody else's
OL,13,Fcrimes.
OL,15,F"I will take responsibility for the
OL,16,Fthings I do, the decisions I make. I'm
OL,17,Fsitting here with you right now,
OL,18,Fanswering questions because I believe
OL,19,Fstrongly in that accountability.
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
