PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780229466
OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: I feel I am serving a
OL,4,Csentence for a crime I did not commit
OL,6,F"But I am not responsible for the
OL,7,Fcrimes that my former husband
OL,8,Fcommitted and I'm not going to
OL,9,Fapologise for somebody else's crimes."
OL,11,FMs Sturgeon previously said she had
OL,12,Fbeen "completely cleared and
OL,13,Fexonerated" by police and that she had
OL,14,Fbeen lied to by her former husband.
OL,16,F"(Murrell) perpetrated a crime on the
OL,17,FSNP," she told the BBC.
OL,19,F"By definition, that included me as
OL,20,Fthe party leader. He misled. He
OL,21,Fdeceived.
