OL,3,CNicola Sturgeon: I feel I am serving a
OL,4,Csentence for a crime I did not commit
OL,6,F"He is serving and will be serving a
OL,7,Fsentence for a crime he committed. I'm
OL,8,Fout here feeling as if I'm serving a
OL,9,Fsentence for a crime I did not commit."
